messages.msg: Welcome to FightLust.com! How can we support you in your journey towards healing today?
I want to quit watching porn
Struggling with pornography or sexual addiction? We're here to offer guidance and prayer. How can we assist you?
Need someone to talk to? We offer confidential support. Tell us how you're feeling, and let's work through this together.
I'm very sad and worried my dad is a pastor too

I'm sorry to hear that you're feeling sad and worried. It's understandable to have these feelings, especially when it involves family. Would you like to share more about what's been troubling you? We're here to listen and support you.
When I watch it I feel guilty

Feeling guilty after watching pornography is a common experience, and it's a sign that you want to make a change. Remember, focusing on Christ can help you find freedom from these struggles. Would you like guidance on how to pray about your struggles or resources to help you on this journey?
It's great that you're seeking help! Would you like me to share some prayers or scriptures that can guide you in your journey towards healing and purity?

Here‚Äôs a prayer that can help you in your journey:

Heavenly Father, we come before your throne room today through the blood of Jesus Christ. We come boldly and with confidence. Your Word says that when we confess our sins, you are faithful and forgive our sins and cleanse us from all unrighteousness. Today, we are praying against the Spirit of lust and all other sexual sins. We break all curses of lust and command all spirits of loneliness and perversion to come out in the name of Jesus Christ. We receive the Spirit of holiness in our lives now to walk in sexual purity.

Feel free to use this prayer as a guide, and remember that you can always reach out for support. If you need more specific resources or prayers, just let me know!
You're welcome! If you have any more questions or need further support, feel free to reach out. We're here for you. Remember, you're not alone in this journey!
You're in our thoughts and prayers. If there's anything else you need or want to talk about, just let me know!
